          </div>

          <aside class="my-12 border-l-4 border-[#13342D] pl-6 py-4 bg-[#E8E6E1] rounded-r-[12px] p-6">
            <p class="text-[22px] md:text-[26px] leading-[1.3] text-[#3F261F] mb-3" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif; font-style:italic; font-weight:300;">
              "We stopped pricing by intuition. RevPAR moved 23%, and I got my Sunday nights back."
            </p>
            <cite class="font-bold uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[2px] text-[#8F6E62] not-italic">— Sarah, Blueridge Retreats</cite>
