            <h4 class="text-[22px] text-[#3F261F] mb-1" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif; font-weight:400;">federico zimerman</h4>
            <div class="font-bold uppercase text-[9px] tracking-[2px] text-[#8F6E62] mb-4">Founder · RevFactor</div>
            <p class="text-[14px] leading-[1.6] text-[#76574C] mb-4">Federico spent 10 years in airline revenue management before applying those principles to short-term rentals. RevFactor's pricing strategies are battle-tested across 165+ properties in 24 states.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/federico-zimerman-23ab3345/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#C8C4BC] text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-[#3F261F] hover:border-[#3F261F] transition-colors">Follow on LinkedIn</a>
              <a href="/journal" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#C8C4BC] text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-[#3F261F] hover:border-[#3F261F] transition-colors">More essays</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="md:sticky md:top-24 md:self-start md:pl-6 md:border-l border-[#C8C4BC]">
        <h5 class="font-bold uppercase text-[9px] tracking-[2.5px] text-[#8F6E62] mb-4">In this essay</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5" id="toc">
